<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />May he live! May the gold of Sheba be given to him.</para>

<para style="q1">May people always pray for him;</para>

<para style="q1">may God bless him all day long.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />May there be abundance of grain in the land;</para>

<para style="q1">on the mountaintops may their crops wave.</para>

<para style="q1">May the fruit of it be like Lebanon;</para>

<para style="q1">may the people flourish in the cities like the grass of the field.</para>
